41:14.481 --> 41:16.014
All the luggage is prepared, sir.

41:16.016 --> 41:18.066
[Indistinct chatter]

41:18.068 --> 41:18.568
â™ª

41:28.244 --> 41:30.612
Hank.

41:30.614 --> 41:31.114
â™ª

41:38.923 --> 41:43.125
I appreciate you coming out here
to see us off.

41:43.127 --> 41:48.380
Just out of curiosity,
does your offer still stand?

41:48.382 --> 41:51.266
You <i>can</i> take the Hank out of Hankmed?

41:51.268 --> 41:54.252
Hankmed has another doctor,

41:54.254 --> 41:56.605
one I trust completely.

41:56.607 --> 41:58.857
He's agreed to run the practice
while I'm away.

41:58.859 --> 42:01.109
This is quite spontaneous of you, Hank.

42:01.111 --> 42:02.945
Will they survive?

42:02.947 --> 42:05.147
They'll be fine.

42:05.149 --> 42:08.367
The question is, will I?

42:08.369 --> 42:10.602
I need some time away.

42:10.604 --> 42:12.404
I need some distance,

42:12.406 --> 42:14.489
some perspective.

42:14.491 --> 42:15.791
And as hard as it may be,

42:15.793 --> 42:18.744
I need to appreciate
that everything will be okay

42:18.746 --> 42:20.329
even if I'm not around.

42:20.331 --> 42:23.114
I see.

42:23.116 --> 42:25.334
This would be different
from our arrangement

42:25.336 --> 42:26.552
up until now, Hank.

42:26.554 --> 42:28.921
In what way?

42:28.923 --> 42:30.389
At this point,

42:30.391 --> 42:32.457
I'm not interested
in sharing you anymore.

42:32.459 --> 42:34.059
I would need a full commitment.

42:34.061 --> 42:37.930
[Helicopter approaches]

42:42.518 --> 42:45.904
Any idea when you'll be back?

42:45.906 --> 42:47.138
Maybe next summer?

42:47.140 --> 42:49.074
And maybe not.

42:58.785 --> 43:01.036
How long till we leave?

43:01.038 --> 43:02.254
How fast can you pack?

43:02.256 --> 43:06.174
I've always traveled light.

